    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Solid good-condition example that appears complete, presentable, and ready to enjoy as a driver. The paint, trim, and interior all show well overall, with the kind of light cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections you\u2019d expect from a car that has been used and maintained rather than hidden away. It comes across as an honest, well-kept car that should make a satisfying driver for someone who wants something attractive and usable without paying mint-condition money. A buyer should expect a clean, enjoyable car with good overall presentation, while understanding it is not flawless and will have the normal minor signs of age and use.",
