    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers dependable transportation value for someone seeking an inexpensive option with plenty of practical use left. A smart choice for a handy buyer, commuter, or project-minded shopper who appreciates straightforward value at an accessible price. Priced to sell and worth a look if affordability is your top priority.",
