    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little budget-friendly car that\u2019s priced for someone who wants affordable wheels without the big upfront cost. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it\u2019s a solid option for a handy buyer, first-time driver, or anyone after a cheap runabout or project. If you\u2019re looking for something straightforward, approachable, and easy on the wallet, this one could be well worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Reliable budget-friendly driver with strong project or commuter potential. Starts up, runs, and offers a solid platform for someone who appreciates a simple, serviceable setup. The powertrain feels usable around town, and the chassis delivers the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes upkeep more approachable. Cosmetically it shows age and wear, but for the money this is an affordable way into a running vehicle with practical utility. Ideal for a buyer looking for basic transportation, a weekend fixer, or a parts-friendly platform with plenty of life left for the right owner.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
